726616f-b.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 72nd Road
726616f-b.text:
Flushing Meadows Park (Queens): The lower end of the park, with its salt meadows and the car barns of the Independent System Subway, seen in a souutheasterly direction from near Grand Central
Parkway and 72nd Road.
October 1, 1935
Views 11,2,3
P. L. Sperr
